---
import Base from "@/layouts/Base.astro";
---
<Base
  title="GPT Breeze — AI productivity shortcuts in your tab"
  description="Save time with AI summaries, tab management, and one‑click shortcuts for YouTube, selected text, and any website."
>
  <link slot="head" rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link slot="head" rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link slot="head" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <meta slot="head" name="theme-color" content="#F6F4F0" />
  <style slot="head">
    :root {
      --bg: #F6F4F0;
      --fg: #22221F;
      --muted: #667085;
      --accent: #22221F;
      --accent-fg: #ffffff;
      --border: #e3e1dc;
      --surface: #ffffff;
      --radius: 14px;
      --maxw: 1120px;
      --header-h: 68px;
    }
    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    body { margin: 0; background: var(--bg); color: var(--fg); font-family: Montserrat, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial; line-height: 1.6; }
    a { color: var(--accent); text-decoration: none; }
    a:hover { opacity: 0.8; }
    .container { max-width: var(--maxw); margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 20px; }
    header { position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 20; background: rgba(246,244,240,0.65); -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(12px) saturate(160%); backdrop-filter: blur(12px) saturate(160%); border-bottom: none; }
    .nav { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; height: var(--header-h); }
    .brand { font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -0.01em; font-size: 1.05rem; }
    .menu { display: flex; gap: 18px; font-size: 0.98rem; align-items: center; }
    .install { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; padding: 10px 16px; border-radius: 999px; border: 1px solid var(--accent); background: var(--accent); color: var(--accent-fg); font-weight: 600; }
    .install.secondary { background: transparent; color: var(--fg); }
    .hero { position: relative; overflow: hidden; padding: calc(120px + var(--header-h)) 0 80px; margin-top: calc(-1 * var(--header-h)); border-top: none; }
    .bg { z-index:99; position: absolute; inset: -20% -20% auto -20%; height: 60vh; background: radial-gradient(60% 60% at 20% 30%, rgba(75,183,215,0.3) 0%, rgba(75,183,215,0) 60%), radial-gradient(50% 50% at 80% 0%, rgba(246,244,240,0.9) 0%, rgba(246,244,240,0) 60%); filter: blur(40px); opacity: 0.8; pointer-events: none; }
    .hero h1, .display { font-size: clamp(2.6rem, 6vw, 4.25rem); line-height: 1.05; margin: 0 0 16px; letter-spacing: -0.02em; text-align: center; }
    .em { font-style: italic; font-weight: 400; }
    .hero p.lead { color: var(--muted); font-size: clamp(1.05rem, 1.5vw, 1.2rem); margin: 0 0 28px; }
    .hero-actions { display:flex; gap:14px; justify-content:center; margin: 50px 0 40px; }
    .btn { display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:8px; padding: 12px 18px; border-radius:999px; font-weight:600; border:1px solid var(--accent); }
    .btn.primary { background: var(--accent); color: var(--accent-fg); }
    .btn.outline { background: transparent; color: var(--fg); }
    .hero-media { display:flex; justify-content:center; margin-top: 80px; }
    .device-frame { width: min(1100px, 100%); border-radius: 24px; border: 1px solid #d0cecd7d; overflow: hidden; position: relative; }
    .ratio { aspect-ratio: 16 / 10; position: relative; width: 100%; }
    /* Lightweight YouTube with poster */
    .yt-lite { position: absolute; inset: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; background-position: center; background-size: cover; cursor: pointer; }
    .yt-lite > .play { cursor:pointer; position: absolute; inset: 0; margin: auto; width: 72px; height: 72px; border-radius: 999px; border: 0; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.9); display: grid; place-items: center; z-index: 1; box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(16,24,40,0.25); }
    .yt-lite > .play::before { content: ""; display: block; width: 0; height: 0; border-left: 18px solid #000; border-top: 12px solid transparent; border-bottom: 12px solid transparent; margin-left: 4px; }
    .yt-lite.loading .play { opacity: 0; pointer-events: none; }
    .grid { display: grid; gap: 16px; grid-template-columns: repeat(12, 1fr); }
    section { padding: 40px 0; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); scroll-margin-top: calc(var(--header-h) + 16px); }
    .card { background: #fff; border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 18px; box-shadow: 0 1px 0 rgba(16,24,40,0.02); }
    .cards { display: grid; gap: 16px; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr)); }
    .muted { color: var(--muted); }
    .kicker { display: inline-block; font-size: 0.8rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.08em; color: var(--accent); font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 10px; background: #EAF7FB; border: 1px solid #D0EEF7; padding: 4px 8px; border-radius: 999px; }
    .list { margin: 8px 0 0 0; padding-left: 18px; }
    .list li { margin: 6px 0; }
    details { background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 12px 14px; }
    summary { cursor: pointer; font-weight: 600; }
    footer { padding: 24px 0 48px; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.95rem; background: transparent; }
    .two { display: grid; gap: 16px; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)); }
    .price { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 800; }
    .strike { text-decoration: line-through; opacity: 0.6; font-weight: 600; }
    .section-title { margin: 0 0 8px; font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 2vw, 2rem); letter-spacing: -0.01em; }
    .subtle { font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--muted); margin: 0 0 16px; }
    .inline { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; }
    .stack { display: grid; gap: 8px; }
    .center { text-align: center; }
  </style>

  <header>
    <div class="container nav">
      <div class="brand">GPT Breeze</div>
      <nav class="menu" aria-label="Main Navigation">
        <a href="#home">Home</a>
        <a href="#guide">Guide</a>
        <a href="#features">Features</a>
        <a href="#privacy">Privacy policy</a>
        <a href="#issues">Issue report</a>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>

  <section id="home" class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="bg"></div>
      <h1 class="display">
        Save <span class="em">hours</span>
        consuming long content on the web
      </h1>
      <p class="lead center" style="max-width: 720px; margin-inline:auto;">
        GPT Breeze Extension summarizes YouTube videos and articles, accelerates your writing, by saving your prompts as one-click shortcuts.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a class="btn primary" href="#pricing">Add to Chrome for free</a>
      </div>

      <div class="hero-media">
        <div class="device-frame">
          <div class="ratio">
            <div
              class="yt-lite"
              data-yt-id="BbCnw9iSvVc"
              aria-label="Play product overview video"
              style="background-image:url('/media/hero/gpt-breeze-hero-video-placeholder-1280x800.jpg')"
              tabindex="0"
            >
              <button class="play" aria-label="Play video"></button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="features">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Features</h2>
      <p class="subtle">AI manages tabs, summarizes content, and speeds your workflow.</p>

      <div class="cards" style="margin-top:12px;">
        <div class="card stack">
          <h3>AI manages your browser tabs/history/bookmarks</h3>
          <p class="muted">Let AI help you organize your browser:</p>
          <ul class="list">
            <li>“Sort my open tabs in logical order”</li>
            <li>“Show me bookmarks about product management”</li>
            <li>“Bookmark those Reddit tabs for digest later”</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="muted">Perfect for taming tab overload and staying focused.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card stack">
          <h3>Summarize YouTube videos</h3>
          <p>Navigate videos with clickable, time‑stamped sections. Extract the full transcript or create a custom AI shortcut for the video.</p>
          <p class="muted">Demonstration: free YouTube long‑video summarizer Chrome extension.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card stack">
          <h3>Web page summarization and chat</h3>
          <p>Get concise bullet‑point summaries and ask follow‑up questions to explore deeper without losing time.</p>
          <p class="muted">Demonstration: website long‑article summarizer Chrome extension.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card stack">
          <h3>Assist your creation process</h3>
          <p>Highlight text to get explanations, translations, or summaries. Improve your writing in one click.</p>
          <p class="muted">Free ChatGPT Chrome extension to improve writing and translate selected text.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card stack">
          <h3>Use different AI models</h3>
          <p>Instantly switch between popular AI models inside GPT Breeze to maximize strengths as needed.</p>
          <p class="muted">GPT‑4.1 Nano is impressively fast for summaries. Claude Sonnet 4 excels at coding and complex reasoning.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="reviews">
    <div class="container two">
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Customers' reviews</h3>
        <p class="muted">Reviews from Chrome Web Store</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>&nbsp;</h3>
        <p class="muted">Reviews from Gumroad</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="pricing">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Pricing</h2>
      <div class="two" style="margin-top:12px;">
        <div class="card stack">
          <h3>Free</h3>
          <div class="price">$0 <span class="muted" style="font-size:0.9rem; font-weight:600;">USD</span></div>
          <ul class="list">
            <li>Unlimited usage of AI shortcuts (BYOM)</li>
            <li>AI shortcuts for YouTube videos</li>
            <li>AI shortcuts for selected text</li>
            <li>AI shortcuts for any website</li>
            <li>(Lots of) future updates</li>
